description:
At James M. Setters, Attorney at Law, we know every legal case is personal. At our Dalton, Georgia, law office, we handle cases that involve bankruptcy, injury and family law. In each of these matters, we know what is at stake. It can be overwhelming when your finances and future are called into question. As an experienced team, we are prepared to do everything in our power to bring you peace of mind and achieve the best results possible.

The founder of our law office, James "Jack" Setters, has spent more than 20 years overseeing bankruptcy cases that include:

  • Chapter 7
  • Chapter 13
  • Debtor-creditor issues

Mr. Setters has filed thousands of petitions over the course of his career. He knows how to minimize the impact of these situations on you so you can focus on moving forward. He also takes a compassionate and personalized approach to his practice. He wants to get to know you and understand your goals so he can best help you.

Here, clients come first. Coming to our law office means seeking the help of a team who truly cares. We stand by your side during the difficult moments and steer you on a path that sets you up for success.

We offer free initial consultations.

James M. Setters, Attorney at Law, is a debt relief agency. We help people file for bankruptcy relief under the Bankruptcy Code.
